<%= render partial: 'email/journal_logo_or_name', locals: { journal: @paper.journal } %>
<br><br>

<h1>
  Changes are needed on your Manuscript in <%= @journal.name %>
</h1>

<hr>

<p>Dear <%= @author.full_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Thank you for submitting your manuscript to <%= @journal.name %>.
  Before your submission can proceed through the editorial process,
  please address the following requests:
</p>

<% if @task.letter_text.present? %>
  <%= render partial: 'email/blockquote', locals: {
    text: simple_format(@task.letter_text)
  } %>
<% end %>

<p>
  Your paper has been made editable to enable you to make these
  changes. Please click on the link below which will take you to
  your manuscript. The task “Changes for Author” will be listed on
  the right hand sidebar and will include the requirements listed
  above. When you have completed these requests, you can mark the task
  complete and resubmit.
</p>

<%= render partial: 'email/button', locals: {
  href: client_paper_url(@task.paper),
  text: 'View Manuscript'
} %>

<p>
  Please address these technical requirements at your earliest convenience, preferably within 1-2 days.
</p>

<p>
  If you have any questions feel free to contact us for assistance by replying to this email.
</p>

<hr>

<%= render partial: 'email/journal_signature', locals: { journal: @journal } %>
